# Documentation
# This is a comprehensive forensic triage target that combines KapeTriage and SANS_Triage
# with additional artifacts for Active Directory, DPAPI, and WMI MOF files.
# It is designed to collect the maximum useful artifact set for DFIR investigations.
#
# Compared to KapeTriage, this adds:
#   - Event Trace Logs (ETL), USB device logs, Windows Firewall logs (via CombinedLogs)
#   - WMI/WBEM repository and MOF files
#   - Thumbnail cache
#   - Windows Index Search
#   - Cloud storage metadata
#   - Messaging client data
#   - NTDS.dit (Active Directory)
#   - DPAPI master keys and credentials
#   - Recycle Bin data files ($R, not just $I metadata)
#   - WMI MOF files
